<h3 class='flex justify-between items-center text-18 leading-24 md:pb-12 lg:pb-16 md:h3 md:block md:justify-start'>
Nous vous répondons 7j/7, 24h/24.
<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 14 12" aria-hidden="true" class="md:hidden ml-16 md:hidden ml-16">
